      public RuntimeModelWorker(ParseTree tree, Map<String,String> options, TreeNodeProperties<JiffleType> types, TreeNodeProperties<SymbolScope> scopes)
      Labels the parse tree with Node objects representing elements of the runtime code. Expects that the tree has been previously annotated by an ExpressionWorker.
